statement.tex:
\text{Is the function defined by}\\

f(x) = \begin{cases} 
          x+5,&if \, x \leq 1\\
          x-5,&if  \,x\gt 1 \\
          \end{cases}\\

\text{a continuous function?}

step.reason:
\text{For a function to be continuous at a\\
point it's limits on either sides should be\\
equal to the value of f(x) at that point}
